description: Mahogany paneled walls rise from a dark-stained oak floor.  Just above a bronzed drake sculpture hangs a portrait of Darkstone Castle, and an ebonwood beam ceiling completes the picture.  A gilded maple table and a well-worn wooden rack stand side by side in the middle of the room.
